page.title: 11A Day in my life
page.content: On Saturday morning I got up at 10am I opened my eyes, got out of bed went down and had breakfast, watched television. Then I went upstairs, got dressed, brushed my teeth. Then mum my sister and me went to my grandmas. Afterwards we went to town. First to the butchers then into a fish shop for some fish. Next we went to a vegetable shop, then to the market. Mum looked at curtains I went to the sports shop. Then to Martin Raymonds followed by Cooplands for my dinner. Then into a freezer shop we then we caught the bus home. When we got home i helped my mum wash up. Later I split some logs, mowed the lawn, put some records on then played on my bike, and split some more logs. I watched television then put a video on till 10-45 and went to bed.
